{"tid":1403007,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如組織中資企業員工發聲","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:28.000Z","uid":265248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0805493437723035086530d685883b95f12984","tid":1403007,"uid":265248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"其實香港好多人做緊中資企業，心裡面縱有不滿都唔敢出聲<br />\n<br />\n不如我地組織中資企業員工嘅TG，鼓勵佢地發聲表態重申五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n等政府以及big6知道縱使佢地係中資公司工作，但唔代表佢地認同政府嘅施政，及警方暴力嘅執法，同時強烈要求政府盡快回應市民五大訴求，早日讓社會回復平靜！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回 6.12 暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，不可秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，調查警察濫暴濫權、追究警察開槍責任及元朗警黑勾結<br />\n<br />\n5. 全面落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打覺得呢個建議有得做？覺得有得做嘅話請幫手推 🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83975c0c84a2b5e8e4f693456a789abbe66d0677","tid":1403007,"uid":265248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"2c60982efc67679da3958b2ac03866e3d8f7d4a6","tid":1403007,"uid":8897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcda3834d3350f1e508117087b9c3f303ab32a7f","tid":1403007,"uid":75647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7bc7dfab9278979ada8200fbb891121e90b496","tid":1403007,"uid":265248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"有中資員工可PM"}]}